text: I am saddened to learn of the passing of Dr. Billy Graham. He was a great man, one of the greatest evangelists of our time.

text: It is disappointing that many of my Senate colleagues did not support the Pain-Capable Unborn Child Protection Act. As a cosponsor of the bill, I will continue to fight for #prolife values. #TheyFeelPain
